org.openimaj.experiment.evaluation

Interface AnalysisResult

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdjustedRandomIndexAnalysis, AggregatedCMResult, ClusterStatsAnalysis, CMResult, DecisionAnalysis, FScoreAnalysis, FullMEAnalysis, IREvalResult, NMIAnalysis, PrecisionAtNResult, PurityAnalysis, RandomBaselineClusterAnalysis, RandomBaselineSMEAnalysis, RandomIndexAnalysis, RangedAnalysisResult, ROCResult, SimpleMEAnalysis, TRECResult

    public interface AnalysisResult
    The result of the analysis of raw data.

    AnalysisResults are capable of producing summary and detailed information in the form of a String as well as producing a JasperPrint objects containing a renderable summary and detailed reports.

    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
